@startuml
title 1. Funding Flow

participant "Fiserv" as Fiserv
participant "Monoova Platform" as Monoova
participant "Your Backend" as Backend

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

Fiserv -> Monoova: Deposits settlement funds into your 
 pre-configured Monoova Automatcher account
activate Monoova

Monoova -> Monoova: Processes deposit and credits 
 your primary mAccount balance

Monoova -> Backend: **Webhook Notification** 
 (Event: `InboundDirectCredit` or `NPPReceivePayment`)
activate Backend
note right
  **Webhook Payload:**
  {
    "accountNumber": "YOUR_AUTOMATCHER_ACCOUNT",
    "amount": 50000.00,
    "transactionDate": "...",
    ...
  }
end note

Backend -> Backend: Verify and process webhook
Backend -> Backend: Update internal balance/records (optional)
deactivate Backend

deactivate Monoova

@enduml
